Deletion

There are relatively large deletions in the alignments between the genome and RNA-seq reads.

e.g. matured adults, readID:ERR4570987.12

deletionData_maturedAdults <- read.table("~/biohazard/oikopleura/analysis/data/maturedOikopleuraAdults/deletionLengthDistribution_lastsplitOKI2018_I69_10_ERR4570987.txt")
